{"tid":2134093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首：倘今屆立法會可延續　未處理撥款或不需重新審議","createTime":"2020-07-31T12:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T13:00:26.000Z","uid":66324,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0060318bbfe4912b97fc262e21d3575ad91cae","tid":2134093,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T12:48:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541123-20200731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541123-20200731.htm&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=c2f0e872\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541123-20200731.htm&h=fd040e31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541123-20200731.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，立法會有年度周期，如果今屆立法會可以延續，未能處理的法案及撥款，可能不需重新審議，包括財委會大量未通過的項目，可以繼續在立法會處理。"},{"pid":"2e1b2ec0d12e2bf8bb45d585bdf0d0019d7d2470","tid":2134093,"uid":162811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73d81c3a7ca1268b183a81e5a840d3bb95d90ea3","tid":2134093,"uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"明日大嶼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b488a12b4553d8bbbf3b6f9aec4d775a5f98d7bb","tid":2134093,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">明日大嶼</span>"},{"pid":"1962f15a69e30bc0f0960a03e465b8d6f5515e07","tid":2134093,"uid":37058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"原來目的係咁"},{"pid":"712a245d784b5ab4124e4fcc3696153650b60c80","tid":2134093,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b488a12b4553d8bbbf3b6f9aec4d775a5f98d7bb","tid":2134093,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07